description.en: Yinbi is an unblockable cryptocurrency, launching on a live network of over 6M users and nodes worldwide. Yinbi conducts instantaneous and safe international transfers, with low handling fees. Yinbi is also launching Yinshi, a peer-to-peer international C2C exchange and marketplace that allows users to trade virtual goods using Yinbi, BTC, ETH, USDT, and more. Yinbi and Yinshi protect privacy and are easy to use. Yinbi not only is decentralized, but also uses traffic obfuscation to intelligently connect nodes, so Yinbi cannot be blocked.
